GET         /quick-calculation                       uk.gov.hmrc.payetaxcalculatorfrontend.controllers.QuickCalcController.redirectToTaxCodeForm

GET         /quick-calculation/tax-code              uk.gov.hmrc.payetaxcalculatorfrontend.controllers.QuickCalcController.showTaxCodeForm
